OL,2,MBuilding an MRI scanner for under £5k
OL,4,CJohn Ginger
OL,5,CFri 19:00-19:30
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GI built an MRI scanner. In my garage.
OL,9,GAnd it actually works. A year ago I
OL,10,Gdecided to find out if you could build
OL,11,Gan MRI machine from off-the-shelf
OL,12,Gparts, at home, without a physics PhD
OL,13,Gor a hospital budget. Spoiler: you
OL,14,Gcan. This is the story of that
OL,15,Gjourney; the moments where it all
OL,16,Gclicked, the moments where it
OL,17,Gabsolutely did not, and everything I
OL,18,Gwish someone had told me before I
OL,19,Gstarted. I'll walk you through the
OL,20,Gphysics of how MRI actually works (I
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
